<svg width="256" height="256" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <defs>
      <style>@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Major+Mono+Display");</style>
    </defs>
    <style>
      text {
        font-family: "Major Mono Display", monospace;
        font-size: 50px;
        fill: #c00;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
    </style>
    <rect x="0" y="0" width="100%" height="100%" style="fill: #222;"></rect>
    <text dominant-baseline="middle" text-anchor="middle" x="50%" y="50%">
      <tspan><D</tspan><tspan style="fill: #fff">E</tspan><tspan>V></tspan>
    </text>
  </svg>
